high_descs: Turn around and walk past the bed, then turn right and go to the night stand on the right side of the bed.
Pick up the pencil on the right side of the night stand.
Move over to the front of the desk on your right.
Place the pencil on the yellow object on the desk.
Turn around and go past the bed, turn right and go to the dresser beneath the window.
Pick up the pencil on the back, right side of the dresser.
Turn around and go past the bed, turn right and go back to the desk across from you.
Place the pencil on the left side of the desk, by the keys.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the end table on the right of the bed.
Pick up the white pencil on the top of the end table.
Move over right to the front of the desk.
Place the white pencil on the top of the yellow lid.
Turn around and go to the front of the wooden dresser on the right.
Pick up the white pencil behind the on the dresser.
Turn right and go back to the front of the desk.
Place the white pencil on the top of the keys on the front left corner of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Move two pencils to the desk.

high_descs: Turn around then face your bedside table on your left.
Take the pencil from the bedside table in front of you.
Turn right and face the desk on your left.
Place the pencil on the desk in front of you.
Turn around and face the cabinet to your right.
Take the pencil on top of the cabinet in front of you.
Turn around then face the desk on your left.
Place the pencil on the desk in front of you.
